collections.description: Look for all the column heading or data field names in a spreadsheet or set of spreadsheets. The column headings are usually at the top of the spreadsheet. There may be multiple sheets in each spreadsheet, so if the returned field name must include the sheet name, e.g. "Deferreds.Total Pension".
